author: Wells Dusenbury
title: Palm Beach Lakes knocks off Ely on Wyatt's game-winner - Sun Sentinel
text:
Palm Beach Lakes knocks off Ely on Wyatt's game-winner Palm Beach Lakes tops Blanche Ely on last-second shot 
Palm Beach Lakes senior Daiquan Wyatt hits the game-winning bucket with less then six seconds left to help the Rams knock off defending state champion Blanche Ely 64-62. Wyatt and coach Lorenzo Hands talk about the big win afterward.
